Create an imodeint for implicit time-steppers. Add the following algorithms to those modules:

(1) Euler's Method -> exodeint
(2) Predictor-corrector Method -> exodeint
(3) Backwards Euler's Method -> imodeint
(4) Crank-Nicolson Method -> imodeint
(5) Douglas-Rachford ADI -> imodeint
(6) Peaceman-Rachford ADI -> imodeint
(7) Exponential Time-Differencing (ETD) -> exodeint
(8) Beylkin-Volsovo's ETD with non-linear part explict & implicit methods -> ?
(9) Trefethen's ETD-RK4 -> exodeint
